16 bit architecture
little endian

signed integers

instruction set:
each instruction is 16 bits

Registers:
- Accumulator:
  - Description: Stores the arithmetic instruction value.


Instruction Set:


- Move Instruction:
  - Opcode: (MOV) 
    0000 0000 0000 0000
  - Operands:
    - Register -> Register you are targetting.
    - Value  -> Value you are writing to specified register.



